### Pattern 3: Schema Index (`schema/index.ts`)
**Found in**: `/Users/jeevanpillay/Code/@lightfastai/lightfast/db/app/src/schema/index.ts`

Two sections: relations first, then a flat re-export of everything from `./tables`:

```ts
export {
  gatewayInstallationsRelations,
  // ...other relations
} from "./relations";

export {
  type InsertOrgRepoIndex,
  type OrgRepoIndex,
  orgRepoIndexes,
  // ... all other table types and objects
} from "./tables";
```

