### Pattern 4: Top-Level DB Index (`db/app/src/index.ts`)
**Found in**: `/Users/jeevanpillay/Code/@lightfastai/lightfast/db/app/src/index.ts`

Re-exports everything from `./schema` plus `{ db }` from `./client` and utilities from `./utils/*`. Relations are exported at this level too (e.g. `gatewayInstallationsRelations`). Note: `orgRepoIndexes` and its types appear in `schema/index.ts` but are **not** in `db/app/src/index.ts` — `orgApiKeys` is in `db/app/src/index.ts:47`. This means some tables are wired only to the schema layer, not the package root.

